OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,FThe father of a boy on trial for
OL,7,Fmurder has told a court his son was
OL,8,Fleft "scared" after an incident with
OL,9,Fthe teenage victim a week before the
OL,10,Ffatal stabbing.
OL,12,FThe 15-year-old defendant, who cannot
OL,13,Fbe named because of his age, is
OL,14,Faccused of the murder of Alfie Lewis,
OL,15,Fwho was also 15, in Horsforth, Leeds,
OL,16,Fon 7 November last year.
OL,18,FAlfie died from a stab wound to the
OL,19,Fchest in an incident which took place
OL,20,Fin front of adults and children at the
OL,21,Fend of the school day.
