OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,FThe defendant has accepted causing
OL,7,FAlfie's death but denies murder,
OL,8,Fclaiming he acted in self defence.
OL,10,FGiving evidence on the seventh day of
OL,11,Fthe trial at Leeds Crown Court, his
OL,12,Ffather told the jury his son told him
OL,13,Fsomebody had tried to rob him days
OL,14,Fbefore Alfie's death, but did not
OL,15,Felaborate.
OL,17,FHe said: "He was very scared of
OL,18,Fsomething. I asked him what happened,
OL,19,Fif it was something serious."
