OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,FHe said the boy told him not to call
OL,7,Fpolice about it.
OL,9,FThe teenager has previously told the
OL,10,Fcourt he was scared of Alfie following
OL,11,Fa number of other incidents.
OL,13,FHe admits taking a kitchen knife out
OL,14,Fwith him to school on the day Alfie
OL,15,Fdied and keeping it in the waistband
OL,16,Fof two pairs of trousers he was
OL,17,Fwearing.
OL,19,FHe went home after Alfie was fatally
OL,20,Finjured at the junction of Church Road
OL,21,Fand Church Lane and was arrested.
