OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,FNicholas Lumley KC, defending, told
OL,7,Fthe jury not to make a decision just
OL,8,Fto protect the memory of a boy who was
OL,9,Fno longer alive.
OL,11,FHe said: "Here we are talking about
OL,12,Ftwo children, one is dead, the other
OL,13,Fsitting in court surrounded by guards
OL,14,Fand next to his father."
OL,16,FHe said the 15-year-old had given
OL,17,Fevidence in the witness box for longer
OL,18,Fthan anyone else during the trial.
