OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,F"He did so with eyes of Alfie's family
OL,7,Fand friends burning into his back,"
OL,8,Fsaid Mr Lumley.
OL,10,FThe jury was told that it could have
OL,11,Fbeen the victim Alfie Lewis on trial
OL,12,Ffor murder if a fight with the
OL,13,Fdefendant four months before he died
OL,14,Fhad ended differently.
OL,16,F"Alfie was the most badly behaved boy
OL,17,Fat his school and the only was they
OL,18,Fcould deal with him was to send him
OL,19,Faway to be taught somewhere else," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
