OL,3,CDad of boy accused of murder tells
OL,4,Ctrial son was 'scared'
OL,6,FMr Lumley said the defendant had been
OL,7,Ffrightened of Alfie and had never
OL,8,Fintended to kill him.
OL,10,FHe said when the defendant left Alfie
OL,11,Fin the road he was "a frightened
OL,12,Flittle boy not really knowing what
OL,13,Fhe'd done'.
OL,15,F"There was no attempt to hide the
OL,16,Fknife. Those actions are not
OL,17,Fconsistent with someone who planned
OL,18,Fwhat would happen," he said.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
